<section class="page-shell privacy-policy-page">
  <article class="compact-panel policy-document">
    <header class="policy-document-header">
      <p class="kicker">Privacy</p>
      <h1>Website privacy and cookies</h1>
      <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>About this website</h2>
      <p>dkapptools.com is a public informational website for DK App Tools apps, articles, support, and privacy information.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Public website visitors</h2>
      <p>DK App Tools does not use advertising cookies, marketing cookies, tracking pixels, or third-party ad trackers on this website.</p>
      <p>The website does not currently have public user accounts, a public contact form, public file uploads, or newsletter signup.</p>
      <p>The website does not include advertising scripts.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Search</h2>
      <p>Search on the website is static and runs in the browser. Search only covers public pages already available on dkapptools.com.</p>
      <p>Search queries are not sent to DK App Tools. Search does not use cookies, localStorage, sessionStorage, analytics, or tracking.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Admin area</h2>
      <p>The website may include an admin area used by DK App Tools to manage site content such as articles.</p>
      <p>Admin login or session features may use strictly necessary authentication or security cookies or tokens. These admin features are for authorized DK App Tools site management and are not used to track public visitors.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>DK App Tools may use privacy-preserving site analytics to understand basic website traffic and page visits, such as Cloudflare Web Analytics or analytics available in the Cloudflare dashboard.</p>
      <p>When analytics are used, DK App Tools prefers privacy-preserving analytics that do not use advertising cookies or cross-site tracking.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Hosting and security</h2>
      <p>The website is hosted through Cloudflare Pages.</p>
      <p>Cloudflare may process standard technical request data when pages are requested. Depending on Cloudflare protection settings, Cloudflare may also use strictly necessary security or traffic-management cookies.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Email contact</h2>
      <p>If you contact DK App Tools by email, you voluntarily send your email address and message content to DK App Tools. Email is used to read and respond to your message and to maintain appropriate support or business records.</p>
      <p>Do not send passwords, access codes, recovery information, private files, or sensitive personal data by email.</p>
      <p>For privacy questions, contact DK App Tools at <a href="mailto:dkapps.support@proton.me">dkapps.support@proton.me</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Cookie banner</h2>
      <p>DK App Tools does not add a cookie banner or fake cookie preferences for this website because DK App Tools does not use advertising, marketing, or tracking cookies on public website visitors.</p>
      <p>If optional non-essential tracking or advertising cookies are added in the future, this website privacy and cookie information and any required consent behavior should be updated.</p>
    </section>
